{"tid":671971,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"90後窮矮毒少年，努力創造幸福生活的故事","createTime":"2018-05-20T14:45:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T06:43:02.000Z","uid":103458,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac48ddb33202f5b34670b689a380f164c4f85ee","tid":671971,"uid":103458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T14:45:36.000Z","msg":"是咁的，有個係香港出世既90後少年<br />\n住係一間溶溶爛爛嘅公屋<br />\n細細個老豆老母日日鬧交，每日一小交三日一大交<br />\n<br />\n小學靠老豆（老豆入面做校工）搭路入左間武館小學，唔係比老師搞就比同學搞<br />\n<br />\n最後好順理成章入埋武館中學，而老豆都包二奶走左，而老母都開始有精神狂，躁狂症日日屋企發癲，學校社工見完家長之後仲話「好彩我專業既野，都唔明你點頂十幾年」<br />\n<br />\n高中dse好努力溫書，人人都屌緊mk妹果時，我屋企仲嘈住唔比我拍靜，朝8 晚6 放學（學校日日補課）番屋企私人補習6-8（躁狂症老母經常在依個時間病發），<br />\n食半個鐘飯，沖下涼，做埋d 19 功課咁就十點幾。你以為咁努力有大學讀？可惜係band3 中學你點努力磨，你都係讀唔掂，垃圾教材 垃圾老師，你係好努力，但你係好努力咁讀緊屎片，最後入埋ive 讀d 95搭8 既垃圾科<br />\n<br />\n搵唔到錢，溝唔到女，ive有個女朋友，結果比港大仔搶埋，人地問讀咩大學果時差d喊出黎，精神病老母仲屌9我無努力讀書<br />\n<br />\n直到最近，我拎曬d錢去旅行，飲酒，叫雞，而岩岩我終於買左psvr，同隻咩我的女朋友既game，準備用針線馮部vr係自己塊面度，以後過住開心幸福既生活！完～"},{"pid":"e55f470f7912a63d1f9fc74d34b4d01079b6a7d6","tid":671971,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T15:07:08.000Z","msg":"巴打好勁"},{"pid":"b72d18ab110aaa21adac49db62f93592d627e30c","tid":671971,"uid":103458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T15:33:27.000Z","msg":"中學時發展路向<br />\n一係唔讀書，但屌女無數<br />\n一係讀書，入大學，但無女屌<br />\n<br />\n而我兩邊都唔到岸，可以跳樓了"},{"pid":"947becd08c27db88dbf565cd7e44d26a12b01635","tid":671971,"uid":179051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:03:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"622c547861f386d6b0536c855f4705be68217742","tid":671971,"uid":103458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"947becd08c27db88dbf565cd7e44d26a12b01635","tid":671971,"uid":179051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b72d18ab110aaa21adac49db62f93592d627e30c","tid":671971,"uid":103458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T15:33:27.000Z","msg":"中學時發展路向<br />\n一係唔讀書，但屌女無數<br />\n一係讀書，入大學，但無女屌<br />\n<br />\n而我兩邊都唔到岸，可以跳樓了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:03:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020c6d01f29007b2323fe37b58137c3063865395","tid":671971,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5f57ef5d3a3b497cd50c79e5c19f6437df061f","tid":671971,"uid":103458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:46:45.000Z","msg":"想死"},{"pid":"71c48055a6bdc2c8e5f2cf1e642e50480dc3ecf5","tid":671971,"uid":70411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:49:37.000Z","msg":"清 番下教會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62f2537d0944a56c47290e179ec4261dea18e2f","tid":671971,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393794e32ddd1f526e37060fe136aca08f2c7c08","tid":671971,"uid":103458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c48055a6bdc2c8e5f2cf1e642e50480dc3ecf5","tid":671971,"uid":70411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:49:37.000Z","msg":"清 番下教會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T20:27:32.000Z","msg":"番完有咩用？出番黎會讀緊大學？銀行存款會增加？有女？"},{"pid":"36d35913bf155ecdd3f9a1dfb3e42550e47b50fb","tid":671971,"uid":103458,"lik